name: Barktoberfest
description:
The Retrievr invites you to discover Barktoberfest, a fall festival for dogs and their people. 
This is the most dog-friendly event in town! So bring your BFF, human or canine, for an afternoon of food, shopping, fun, music, and oh yeah ... locally brewed beer. $10 entry fee (10 and under free).
address:
Old Man's
Address: Pantai Batu Bolong Street No.117X, Canggu, North Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali 80351

name: DockDogs - Big Air
description:
DockDogs World Championship competition comes to Bali!
We want to promote a positive, happy, fun filled experience for dog owners and their dogs through dock dog training and dock jumping activities. The competition is open to all breeds of dogs over 6 months old and all handlers over 7 years of age. We have zero discrimination here. All you need is patience and a healthy dog who has a love for water and strong toy drive. 
Yearly membership fee is $35.00. Meetings are held on the second Sunday of each month.

name: Yoga? I'm down dog!
description: Participants will learn about bonding with their dogs through Doga. While guiding the yoga practice, the Doga instructor will provide moments throughout the class for participants to bond, reward, and breathe with their dogs. The instructor will provide suggested cues for the leash and various opportunities during class to check-in and reconnect with their dogs.

name: Speed Dating with Dogs
description:
Let’s face it, dating in 2019 is hard work even with all the dating apps available.
While men are defeated by fake profiles, limited matches, and no replies, women are overloaded with trying to find that one good guy like a needle in a haystack.
So what about if we eliminated all the bull*hit and help you to find that 'right' one?
Dating with Dogs does exactly that – we bring like-minded people together in a non-confrontational way and add a whole bunch of dogs.
It’s fun, it’s flirty and the fact that they ‘paid’ for a ticket means that they’re genuine.
Grab your ticket NOW and by this time next week, you could be a smitten kitten.
While we encourage people to bring their pups, this dating event is for dog lovers in general, so whether you have a dog or not, you're invited!
address:
La Brisa
Jalan Pantai Batu Mejan, Gang La Brisa Echo Beach, Canggu, North Kuta, Badung, Bali, Indonesia

name: Dogs on boats?
description: Yes! Bring your pooch on a leash and enjoy quality time with your dog while cruising on La Meridian. Sit back, and relax. Keep your dog on your lap, in a seat or on the deck. Our dog cruise boat offers plenty of safe outdoor seating, water bowls and a special newspaper-lined restroom for your pet. Enjoy a great day out of doors with your favorite companion.

name: Movie Night with Your Dog
description: Dog Movie Night is back! Bring your dog/dogs out to enjoy an outdoor movie and socialize with your dog-loving neighbours. Bring lawn chairs, blankets, munchies and non-alcoholic beverages. The movie will start at sundown.

name: Woof, Wag, & Wine Night
description:
Calling all slobbery, happy, wiggly pups for a night of fun, TREATS, and wine!
Whether you have a long tail, short tail, curly tail, or fluffy tail, get it down for Woof, Wag, and Wine night on the first Friday of every month. 
Oh!  And don't forget to bring your human and treat them to a drink or two!

name: Doggy Brunch
description: Eat with your beloved best friend in a special place set up for you and your dog
